Invocation Name: the daily camera
des:
Local Boulder and University of Colorado news from The Daily Camera newspaper. Top News, Business News, Campus News and Campus Sports News are available.

To hear headlines, say:
Ask The Daily Camera for Top News
Ask The Daily Camera for Business News
Ask The Daily Camera for Campus News
Ask The Daily Camera for Campus Sports News

The hear a summary about a story in the current headlines, say "Read the story on" or "Tell me more about" followed by a phrase that contains at least two words in the story headline.
